channel.title: Unknown error
channel.description: I've recently gotten a new computer, and every server I've tried to go on, the clients always give me errors like this: [img]http://i.imgur.com/hvJ5km1.png[/img] Idk if I have to download a certain version of java or something, I'm not the smartest when it comes to tech issues. Anyway. if someone can shed some light on what I have to do to start playin servers on this computer, I would love you.
